soot.jimple.infoflow.methodSummary.handler

Class SummaryTaintPropagationHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.jimple.infoflow.methodSummary.handler.SummaryTaintPropagationHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    soot.jimple.infoflow.handlers.TaintPropagationHandler

    public class SummaryTaintPropagationHandler
extends Object
implements soot.jimple.infoflow.handlers.TaintPropagationHandler
    The SummaryTaintPropagationHandler collects all abstraction that reach the return statement of a specified method.

      • setFollowReturnsPastSeeds

        public void setFollowReturnsPastSeeds(boolean follow)
        Sets whether propagations out of the method to be summaries shall be allowed. If not the analysis will not march up the callgraph any further from that method.
        Parameters:
        follow - True if propagations upwards from the target method shall be allowed, otherwise false
